com.fasterxml.clustermate.api

Class EntryKeyConverter<K extends EntryKey>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.clustermate.api.EntryKeyConverter<K>

  • public abstract class EntryKeyConverter<K extends EntryKey>
extends Object
    Abstract class that defines interface to use for converting "raw" StorableKey instances into higher level key abstractions, constructing such keys, and calculating routing hash codes.
